<section id="fb2">
  <p class="feedbacktext">The percentage in the bar chart at the top referred to two different age groups, for example 31 per cent of 16 to 24 year olds. This pie chart has mixed the age groups together to form a whole, so now the percentages don't refer to anything.</p>
</section>

